# Contact email (public-facing)

MiniMuster public contact info must use the **personal** email only.

## Use

- `jacob.rozell83@gmail.com`
- `mailto:jacob.rozell83@gmail.com`

## Never use

- `jrozell@myocv.com` or any `@myocv.com` address
- Any work or employer email in docs, HTML, or bundled markdown

## Applies to

- `docs/**` (GitHub Pages, App Store URLs)
- `MiniMuster/Resources/**` (in-app Privacy & Accessibility)

When adding or editing contact info, search the repo for `@myocv.com` and `mailto:` before finishing. Keep `docs/` and `MiniMuster/Resources/` in sync when both exist (e.g. `ACCESSIBILITY.md` ↔ `accessibility.html`).
